t = int(input())
while t>0:
    t -= 1
    
    n, k, s = list(map(int, input().split()))
    arr = list(map(int, input().split()))
    temp = sorted(list(range(n)), key=lambda x:arr[x])
    arr.sort()
    ind = n-1
    while ind > 0:
        if arr[ind] > s:
            ind -= 1
        elif arr[ind]+arr[ind-1] > s and arr[ind]+arr[0] <= s:
            temp = temp[ind:ind+1] + temp[:ind] + temp[ind+1:] 
            break
        else:
            break
    ans = [str(i+1) for i in temp]
    print(' '.join(ans))

t = int(input())
while t>0:
    t -= 1
    
    n, k, s = list(map(int, input().split()))
    arr = list(map(int, input().split()))
    temp = sorted(list(range(n)), key=lambda x:arr[x], reverse=True)
    arr = sorted(arr, reverse=True)
    ind = 0
    while ind<n and arr[ind]>s:
        ind += 1
    
    temp = sorted(temp[ind:]) + temp[:ind]
        
    ans = [str(i+1) for i in temp]
    print(' '.join(ans))
